{"tid":1475282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢說話卷 滅廣東話] 大家唔好咁懶，copy template冇用㗎","createTime":"2019-08-15T12:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:37.000Z","uid":269265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa254e640fc1eeb64a9ed078a78eb5c023cdc3c","tid":1475282,"uid":269265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:07:33.000Z","msg":"網上已有意見書template流傳緊。<br />\n但大家唔好咁懶！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抄template只當同一份意見咋！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家如果咁有決心保衛廣東話，<br />\n自己寫一份啦，長短不拘。<br />\n<br />\n其實連登應該有唔少中文教師。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋文筆咁好，又咁清楚說話卷嘅好處，<br />\n唔係咁都唔貢獻一份嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n寫完除咗即刻email去EDB，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最好都擺一份喺呢度，</span></span><br />\n咁其他人要抄都多啲source啦！<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n16/9終止諮詢：<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=7b22fdae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fwhats-new.html&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=f76e9ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=12fc733c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔同意，請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n「遞交意見書時是否提供個人資料，並無硬性規定。"},{"pid":"365f388d29c15962746cfce72d579c6b066aba18","tid":1475282,"uid":106851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:07:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8366fdeb3a1d387cba854267e0331fb05c247789","tid":1475282,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"Copy一份係到就唔好啦 俾人一對就知個ac係對邊個email"},{"pid":"39deeedce52ce2c39b462bd5c00543c6a7794214","tid":1475282,"uid":269265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8366fdeb3a1d387cba854267e0331fb05c247789","tid":1475282,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"Copy一份係到就唔好啦 俾人一對就知個ac係對邊個email"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"巴打又講得有道理。<br />\n咁唯有希望大家生生性性，自己努力啲嘔封意見書喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d17575e4d40795e4d8027dea3cfa157d6495a","tid":1475282,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請減少使用&ldquo;勇武&rdquo; &ldquo;和理非&rdquo;等標籤直接指代人<br />\n大家都係手足，用呢啲形容行為嘅字眼去指代群體好易起分化作用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----分享-----<br />\n[心理戰] 唔好再講和理非 唔好再講勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請不要說推，說<br />\n721 811<br />\n818我會上街<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔做捉鬼敢死隊<br />\n我會一生罷買國貨 直至支爆"},{"pid":"c933718b2196ec9237e5559e66ed6a4dfbde0a88","tid":1475282,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5968cacf4a6c3beec15021e755a499716b6421e0","tid":1475282,"uid":107639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4376ddcf7d25c2bcb358d9742c914a20880c5447","tid":1475282,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9758b7e599a8cfcc67e1850dbbab0d0ec8cf1f1","tid":1475282,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}